This repository is an aiogram boilerplate for team reuse.

Rules:
- Main rules are in docs/AI_INSTRUCTIONS.md — read it first.
- Never create new folders or files outside the existing structure without explaining why first.
- Keep handlers thin — no logic, only Telegram I/O.
- Keep business logic in services/.
- Keep all queries in bot/db/repos.py.
- Never assume a specific database — DB config comes from DATABASE_URL in settings only.
- Never hardcode user-facing strings outside bot/strings/.
- Never build keyboards or buttons inside handlers — use bot/ui/.
- Prefer flat, pragmatic code over extra abstraction.
- Add tests for every service, handler, and DB behavior.
